ion":"> This guide has been converted, and some content may be missing. \n[View the full guide on pred.gg](https://pred.gg/guides/9177Tx6)\n\n#### Immortal Mage Steel offlane build \n---\nThis build makes you incredibly tanky and offers great magical damage that scales with HP.\n\n#### Elafrost alternatives\n---\nUse **Tainted Guard** for physical anti-heal. **Void helm** can be used when you are facing a midlaner on your lane but is also a good option against heroes with **Fire Blossom**. **Bonesaw** is a great item if you face an enemy **Grux** on your lane.\n\n#### Crystalline Cuirass alternatives\n---\n**Wardens Faith** is a nice alternative if you are facing a crit-carry on offlane. If you feel like you are already immortal, **Frosted Lure** is a great item to give your damage another HP-scaling boost. **Stonewall** is strong against all heroes that do their main damage using physical abilities, most notably **Grux**.","hero_id":21,"role":"offlane","crest_id":43,"item1_id":128,"item2_id":126,"item3_id":129,"item4_id":118,"item5_id":194,"item6_id":null,"skill_order":[1,4,2,1,1,3,4,1,4,2,3,1,4,4,2,3,2,2],"upvotes_count":67,"downvotes_count":28,"created_at":"2023-01-27T22:54:31.151826Z","updated_at":"2024-02-13T20:59:42.347561Z","game_version":{"id":56,"name":"v0.14.3","release":"2024-02-06T10:14:32Z","display_badge":false,"created_at":"2024-02-06T10:14:32Z","updated_at":"2024-02-06T10:14:32Z"},"author":"C0re","author_player":null,"modules":[{"title":"Elafrost alternatives","item1_id":176,"item2_id":166,"item3_id":111,"item4_id":null,"item5_id":null,"item6_id":null,"item7_id":null},{"title":"Crystalline Cuirass alternatives","item1_id":163,"item2_id":193,"item3_id":177,"item4_id":null,"item5_id":null,"item6_id":null,"item7_id":null}]},{"id":16586,"title":"The TANKY One","description":"> This guide has been converted, and some content may be missing. \n[View the full guide on pred.gg](https://pred.gg/guides/WIC06Mu)\n\nOfflane Build for Steel.","hero_id":21,"role":